  "name": "RPlog_Danik_s_Trap",
  "title": "Danik's Trap: The Chandrila Jailbreak",
  "summary": "A rebel resistance cell on Chandrila launches an audacious jailbreak on the Imperial prison, infiltrating in stolen Stormtrooper armor under the leadership of Ridge and Fenn while a distraction force with trebuchets, E-webs, and the assault-armored ex-commando Fael Ramsis stands by outside. But Grand Admiral Danik Kreldin has anticipated the strike: as the disguised rebels enter the security corridor, hidden E-webs deploy and Imperial troops spring the ambush, while TIE bombers and fighters strike the rebel artillery and the Imperial agent Dibar and others engage the attackers. A chaotic, bloody battle erupts across the courtyard, with the demolitions expert Sev blowing breaches in the walls, the gunner Private Eoin dying heroically at his E-web, and Sergeant Hoolihan struggling to rally the survivors. Ridge orders a desperate breakout and is gravely wounded; with the assault failing and casualties mounting on both sides, the rebels finally stand down and surrender. Danik survives once more, having sprung his trap with the help of the traitor Fenn, and orders the captives kept alive as bait for Skywalker.",
